If you're encountering an embedding error, please check how you set your Project ID in the `CREATE MODEL` step. A common mistake is leaving the `$` in the Project ID (e.g., `$my-project-id` instead of `my-project-id`), or forgetting to replace `$YOUR_PROJECT_ID` entirely.

Please drop the model and recreate it using the exact code below, making sure to properly replace `YOUR_PROJECT_ID` with your actual Project ID and **NO `$` sign**:

```sql
DROP MODEL TextEmbeddings;

CREATE MODEL TextEmbeddings
INPUT(content STRING(MAX))
OUTPUT(embeddings STRUCT<values ARRAY<FLOAT32>>)\nREMOTE OPTIONS (
    endpoint = '//aiplatform.googleapis.com/projects/YOUR_PROJECT_ID/locations/us-central1/publishers/google/models/text-embedding-004'
);
```
